 you.\u201d Source: H\u0323ilyat al-Awliya\u0304' 2\/218 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u0627\u0635\u0645 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0648\u0644 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0627\u0644\u064a\u0629 \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35573,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/06\/wahb-shahawat-shaytan\/","url_meta":{"origin":31926,"position":1},"title":"Wahb on Shahwah: Satan flees from one who overcomes his desires","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 6, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Muhammad ibn Ziyad reported: Wahb ibn Munabbih, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cWhoever places his lusts beneath his feet, Satan will flee from his shadow. Whoever overcomes his whims by his forbearance, that one is among the victorious scholars.\u201d Source: H\u0323ilyat al-Awliya\u0304\u2019 4\/60 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064f\u062d\u064e\u0645\u0651\u064e\u062f\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0632\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0627\u062f\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31934,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/09\/ibrahim-people-of-whims\/","url_meta":{"origin":31926,"position":2},"title":"Ibrahim on Whims: People of whims never brought any good","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 9, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Hamzah reported: Ibrahim al-Nakha\u2019i, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cBy Allah, I have not seen in what they produce as much good as the weight of a seed,\u201d meaning the people of whims, opinions, and speculation. Source: H\u0323ilyat al-Awliya\u0304' 4\/222 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u062d\u0645\u0632\u0629 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0625\u0628\u0631\u0627\u0647\u064a\u0645 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u062e\u0639\u064a \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31825,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/08\/shabi-whims-whisk-nar\/","url_meta":{"origin":31926,"position":3},"title":"Sha\u2019bi on Whims: Lowly desires whisk their companions to Hellfire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 8, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Shubrumah reported: Al-Sha\u2019bi, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cVerily, whims are only named as such because they whisk their companions away to the Hellfire.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Da\u0304rimi\u0304 398 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0634\u064f\u0628\u0652\u0631\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0634\u0651\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0625\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0633\u064f\u0645\u0651\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0647\u064e\u0648\u064e\u0649 \u0644\u0650\u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u064a\u064e\u0647\u0652\u0648\u0650\u064a \u0628\u0650\u0635\u064e\u0627\u062d\u0650\u0628\u0650\u0647\u0650 \u064a\u0639\u0646\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0627\u0631 398 \u0633\u0646\u0646\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28842,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/08\/masters-knowledge-act-upon\/","url_meta":{"origin":31926,"position":4},"title":"Ibn Salam on &#8216;Ilm: Masters of knowledge act upon what they know","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 8, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Ubaydullah ibn Umar reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said to Abdullah ibn Salam, \u201cWho are the masters of knowledge?\u201d Abdullah said, \u201cThose who act upon what they know.\u201d Umar said, \u201cWhat nullifies knowledge in the hearts of men?\u201d Abdullah said, \u201cGreed.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Da\u0304rimi\u0304 595\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31823,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/08\/ibn-abbas-quran-whims\/","url_meta":{"origin":31926,"position":5},"title":"Ibn Abbas on Whims: The Quran casts blame upon lowly desires","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 8, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn al-Jawzi reported: Ibn Abbas, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cAllah Almighty did not mention whims in any place in his book but that he cast blame on it.\u201d Source: Dhamm al-Hawa\u0301 1\/36 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0648\u0632\u064a \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u